peeds and large <a title="Bandwidth (signal processing)" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bandwidth_%28signal_processing%29">bandwidth</a>; they suffer relatively little <a title="Attenuation" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Attenuation">attenuation</a>, allowing them to cover long distances with few <a title="Repeaters" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Repeaters">repeaters</a>; they are also immune to <a title="Crosstalk" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crosstalk">crosstalk</a> and other forms of <a title="Electromagnetic interference" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electromagnetic_interference">EM interference</a> which plague electrical transmission.<sup id="cite_ref-4"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internet_backbone#cite_note-4">[5]</a></sup>', 'Modern ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '132-revision', '', '', '2012-02-23 01:53:13', '2012-02-23 01:53:13', '', 132, 'http://biogas.trikti.com/132-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
